  "text": "And as an ending question, I will just ask it, is it possible then for the ipsys to have either positive or negative polarity, or must he be neither? I am Ra. We shall respond to the meaning of this term in a especialized sense. The Ipsissimus is one who has mastered the tree of life and has used this mastery for negative polarization. Is there any a brief query which we may respond to as we take leave of this instrument.",
